targets.query:
SELECT mean("value") FROM "ui_group_duration"
WHERE $timeFilter
GROUP BY "group_name", time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT
  count("value") AS "Count",
  min("value") AS "Min",
  mean("value") AS "Avg",
  stddev("value") AS "Stddev",
  percentile("value", 95) AS "P95",
  percentile("value", 99) AS "P99",
  max("value") AS "Max"
FROM "browser_http_req_duration"
WHERE $timeFilter
GROUP BY "name"

SELECT
  count("value") AS "Request Count",
  mean("value") AS "Avg Response Time",
  percentile("value", 50) AS "Median Response Time",
  percentile("value", 75) AS "75th Percentile",
  percentile("value", 90) AS "90th Percentile",
  percentile("value", 95) AS "95th Percentile",
  percentile("value", 99) AS "99th Percentile"
FROM "http_req_duration"
WHERE $timeFilter
GROUP BY "name" fill(null)

SELECT
  sum("value") AS "Error Count",
  ((sum("value") / count("value")) * 100) AS "Error Rate (%)"
FROM "http_req_failed"
WHERE $timeFilter
GROUP BY "name" fill(null)

SELECT
  sum("value") / 5 AS "Throughput (reqs/sec)"
FROM "http_reqs"
WHERE $timeFilter
GROUP BY "name" fill(null)
SELECT min("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0
SELECT max("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 90) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT min("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
